{"tid":1059631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"波音737 MAX傳屢遭投訴    機師：操作手冊「欠妥得近乎犯罪」","createTime":"2019-03-13T08:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T08:33:36.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"099c6ca8b2bdf4d368370bbc04275a32c8795baf","tid":1059631,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:59:34.000Z","msg":"報告內容主要是投訴客機的自動駕駛系統，當中不少都提及客機起飛後爬升時出問題，機頭會突然向下。紀錄顯示有關飛行於去年10月至11月期間進行。<br />\n<br />\n亦有機師投訴客機操作手冊差劣，不足以令機師理解客機。該機師於報告中稱，即使機師不太明白系統，但有一點是明白的，就是該系統非常容易出錯。<br />\n<br />\n有機師直言，機師未受足夠訓練，加上新款737客機的系統與舊款機系統的不同之處未被充分披露，美國當局及有關公司讓機師駕駛，做法「無良心」（unconscionable）。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦航空管理局（Federal Aviation Administration）發聲明回應，稱暫未發現全面的表現問題（systemic performance issues），無理據支持停飛。<br />\n<br />\n美國航空（American Airlines）回應查詢時指，稱相信波音737 Max 8客機安全，未遭遇手動操作時客機角度突然改變的問題，強調旗下機師有足夠訓練。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dallasnews.com/business/airlines/2019/03/12/boeing-737-max-8-pilots-complained-feds-months-suspected-safety-flaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dallasnews.com%2Fbusiness%2Fairlines%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2Fboeing-737-max-8-pilots-complained-feds-months-suspected-safety-flaw&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=6052c4f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dallasnews.com/business/airlines/2019/03/12/boeing-737-max-8-pilots-complained-feds-months-suspected-safety-flaw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/5766398-ASRS-Reports-for-737-max8.html#document/p10/a486269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F5766398-ASRS-Reports-for-737-max8.html%23document%2Fp10%2Fa486269&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=75f4c4cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/5766398-ASRS-Reports-for-737-max8.html#document/p10/a486269</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2TIpiXo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TIpiXo&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=bd06ace7\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2TIpiXo</a>"},{"pid":"52fdf7806ded6d80ca6b88509f08467e33ec9294","tid":1059631,"uid":29178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}